{"type":"question","id":21987,"title":"如何看待国内新疆内大学计划4.10左右开学内地学生3.26返校又随即打脸辟谣？","uid":33165,"topics":[4978,91,330],"contents":"昨晚新疆师范大学连夜发布了返校通知，初步计划于4.10日开学，并要求疆外学生3.26（有说28）返校进行14天隔离。此外，新疆医科大学、新疆财经大学等高校也透露了类似的计划。<br>\n由于通知时间较晚，3.25凌晨通知并要求学生3.26就返校，由于时间仓促和交通资源还未完全恢复的原因，且当下疫情仍未完全缓解，长时间乘坐交通工具存在较大风险，另疆外学生怨声载道。<br>\n但是，但是，随即新疆师范大学又发布了一则“辟谣声明”。令很多刚刚抢到买好车票的同学措手不及。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wbAvzs0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wbAvzs0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wbAvzs0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/xsk8muJ.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xsk8muJ.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xsk8muJ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2AwF8Z.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2AwF8Z.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/D2AwF8Z.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NB0YyKb.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NB0YyKb.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NB0YyKb.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8BwD2T2.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8BwD2T2.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8BwD2T2.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n辟谣声明<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/olW9L33.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/olW9L33.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/olW9L33.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SaKvys6.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SaKvys6.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SaKvys6.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/CjkbNDW.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer no